INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2,1,'2014-09-16 17:32:31','2014-09-16 17:32:31','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://bajlumyuum.com//wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','publish','open','open','','sample-page','','','2014-09-16 17:32:31','2014-09-16 17:32:31','',0,'http://bajlumyuum.com//?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(7,1,'2015-04-05 02:06:01','2015-04-05 02:06:01','','jaguar_warrior_by_gordotote-d4d2o0m','','inherit','closed','closed','','jaguar_warrior_by_gordotote-d4d2o0m','','','2015-04-05 02:06:01','2015-04-05 02:06:01','',0,'http://bajlumyuum.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/jaguar_warrior_by_gordotote-d4d2o0m.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(8,1,'2015-04-05 02:06:16','2015-04-05 02:06:16','http://bajlumyuum.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/cropped-jaguar_warrior_by_gordotote-d4d2o0m.jpg','cropped-jaguar_warrior_by_gordotote-d4d2o0m.jpg','','inherit','closed','closed','','cropped-jaguar_warrior_by_gordotote-d4d2o0m-jpg','','','2015-04-05 02:06:16','2015-04-05 02:06:16','',0,'http://bajlumyuum.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/cropped-jaguar_warrior_by_gordotote-d4d2o0m.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(11,1,'2015-04-13 17:34:36','2015-04-13 17:34:36','<p>\r\n Oír hablar a este hombre me desmonta. Yo quiero escribir como él. Me gusta su sencillez, la ternura que despiertan sus palabras cuando habla con esa calma suya,  esa mirada inteligente, su sensibilidad para ver lo esencial en lo cotidiano. Me gusta cómo se detiene en explicar el sufrimiento de las gentes más sencillas, cómo da voz a los sin voz. Y me doy cuenta que mejor no tirar la toalla, porque aún hay personas que van más allá de su propio ego, y se funden con el universo y lo hacen suyo cuando lo miran, y cuando nos lo cuentan.\r\nGracias Eduardo Galeano por ser una prueba de que no todo está perdido y que hay personas que valen la pena.\r\n</p>\r\n<strong>Referencia</strong><a href=\"http://soniagigu.blogspot.mx/2014/12/vivir-sin-miedo-de-eduardo-galeano.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Texto:: Sonia Giménez</a>\r\n<iframe width=\"420\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rygqfWagvhQ\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>','Eduardo Galeano - Vivir sin Miedo','','publish','closed','closed','','eduardo-galeano-vivir-sin-miedo','','','2015-06-02 17:00:23','2015-06-02 17:00:23','',0,'http://bajlumyuum.com/?p=11',0,'post','',0),(12,1,'2015-04-13 17:34:36','2015-04-13 17:34:36','<iframe width=\"420\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rygqfWagvhQ\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>','Eduardo Galeano - Vivir sin Miedo','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2015-04-13 17:34:36','2015-04-13 17:34:36','',11,'http://bajlumyuum.com/2015/04/13/11-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(13,1,'2015-05-27 15:55:41','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','closed','closed','','','','','2015-05-27 15:55:41','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://bajlumyuum.com/?p=13',0,'post','',0),(14,1,'2015-05-27 16:16:22','2015-05-27 16:16:22','','jaguar','','inherit','closed','closed','','jaguar','','','2015-05-27 16:16:22','2015-05-27 16:16:22','